name: Laharl
description: He's the heir of the Overlord. The so called fiercest demon in the Netherworld. But he's not good at dealing with busty women.

name: Killia
description: Supported by his friends, Killia has overcome his anger and sadness. No longer confused, his true power has already awakened.

name: Valvatorez
description: This young vampire is a Prinny Instructor. His favorite thing in is sardines. It's said that he's actually a very influential being.

name: Adell
description: He is a good young man who places great value on family. He has his own "style" and yields to no one. It is said that he is dating Rozalin.

name: Mao
description: He's the current Dean of Evil Academy. He has an EQ of 1.8 million and loves conducting evil research. He's also a remodeling maniac who loves to drizzle soy sauce on omelets.

name: Etna
description: She's Laharl's vassal and is known for her caustic tongue. She is a great admirer of the late King Krichevskoy. She runs through Prinnies as if they were paper napkins.

name: Fallen Angel Flonne
description: A former Apprentice Angel who fell from heaven for the crime of injuring another Angel. A love freak and Tokusatsu aficionado. Devoted to spreading the word of love, with somewhat mixed results...

name: Seraphina
description: The Gorgeous Overlord who has overcome her fear of poverty. Thanks to her newfound strength, she has become a fearless character. She has subtle romantic feelings for Killia.

name: Fuka
description: A middle school girl half transformed into a Prinny. She is unconvinced of her own death and thinks she's dreaming. She likes to rampage around with Desco.

name: Rozalin
description: A naive young lady. Now, she's learning all about the outside world, while living in harmony with Adell.

name: Axel
description: A family-oriented dark hero... and a dunce. He's got quite a lot of die hard fans who love his fanciful delusions and positive attitude when facing difficulties.

name: Fenrich
description: A young werewolf who serves Valvatorez. He has many schemes to improve his Master's position. "All is for my Lord" is his catchphrase.

name: Majorita
description: The Witch Who Controls Death, a former Demon General. She looks like a child, but her power rivals that of an Overlord.

name: Emizel
description: The only son of Hugo, the former President of the Netherworld. In order to become the President, he's busy doing his job as Death.

name: Barbara
description: A demon who was once an Overlord Candidate. The type of person who takes pride in faithfully carrying out orders, but is not good at acting on their own will.

name: Girl Laharl
description: Isn't it a tragedy?! A female Laharl. But the same autocratic egotist all the same. Her popularity has been soaring since the transformation.

name: Christo
description:
An Overlord from the Giant Netherworld... at least that is what he said.
As a peerless counselor and strategist,
he will do whatever it takes to achieve his goal.

name: Zeroken
description: An Overlord who has overcome his cowardice and timidness. An easily elated Ultimate Demon Technique user. He admires Killia as his senior disciple.

name: Red Magnus
description: The Overlord of Scorching Flame, where ruffians gather. He loves to say "Super", and has a super boorish personality. However, he also has a gentle side and cares for his subordinates.

name: Krichevskoy
description: Laharl's father, the Overlord who once ruled another Netherworld. He has regained the power he had in his prime.

name: Sicily
description: This girl is an angel from Celestia. She is strong-minded and hardworking, and good at cooking. It's said she likes Prinnies a lot.

name: Almaz
description: The Hero Wannabe has grown into a true Hero. Despite his cowardice, he's still practicing the "Hero's Oath". The Newly Married Hero!

name: Master Big Star
description: A glittering, brilliant, big star. The "Master" is not a term of endearment, it's part of his real name.

name: Salvatore
description:
The No.3 delinquent student in the Evil Academy, and one of the legendary "Diez Gentleman".
She loves to force others to carry out her whimsical orders,
and very few can complete what she asks.

name: Sapphire
description: The princess of a human kingdom. She's still the "Killing Machine"  despite being married to Almaz. Her goal is to become "the strongest creature on earth."

name: Nemo
description: A soul born from hatred toward humans. Controlled by Fear the Great. It creates malice, and uses this malice to gain more power.

name: Bloodis
description: Former Demon General once known as the Great Demon Fist. His fists, which he uses with overwhelming power, can crush anything that stands in his way.

name: Nagi
description: She is a 14-year-old girl who utilizes mechanical techniques left behind by her father. She has a strong will to end all war.

name: Rutile
class_name_4: Transfer Student from the Human World
description: A kind girl who's a human-Nekomata hybrid. She possesses super strength despite her slender appearance.

name: Stella
class_name_3: The ONLY Daughter of the Dean
class_name_4: Class Representative of the Majin Academy
class_name_5: Slaughter Union President of the Majin Academy
description: The daughter of a Majin who likes pulling pranks. She has really unique taste and fancies slimes and zombies.

name: Xenolith
description: A taciturn young demon. He has extraordinary magical power  and such a cold attitude that no one dares to approach him.

name: Apprentice Angel Flonne
description: An Apprentice Angel who respects Seraph Lamington. She becomes a companion of Laharl for her missionary work: spreading the ideals of universal love.

name: Pure Flonne
description: Flonne's awakened Archangel form, overflowing with the power of belief. The force of great love  has improved her abilities!

name: Archangel Flonne
class_name_5: The Best Archangel of All Time
description: An amazing Archangel who unites the angels in Celestia. A love freak and Tokusatsu aficionado.

name: Void Dark
description:
The most powerful Overlord who
brought all Netherworlds into war and has a troubled past with Killia.
To him, his sister's smiling face is his most precious treasure.

name: Artina
description: An Angel tasked by Celestia to collect money from the Netherworld. Doing her job too well has resulted in  Demons calling her the "Angel of Avarice".

name: Sister Artina
description: Artina when she was still alive as a human. Pure and innocent, she's saved the lives of countless soldiers.

name: Tyrant Valvatorez
description: A powerful vampire with the name of "Tyrant". He thinks the mission of demons is to strike fear into human hearts, and he takes pride in it. His goal is to become the avatar of terror.

name: Awakened Killia
description:
Killia, who has overcome his confusions and destructive urges,
and pushed the Ultimate Demon Technique
to its true limits.

name: Tyrant Overlord Killidia
description: Killia's visage when he was possessed by destructive impulses. Known as the Tyrant Overlord, he gives out  a terrifying evil aura that keeps others away.

name: Etna (2P)
description: It's still not bad  even with the difference in stats. Without this [Basic] understanding, it wouldn't be Etna (2P).

name: Majin Etna
description: Majin from another Netherworld. Her power rivals that of an Overlord. Her vicious roasts can burn people to a crisp.

name: Heroine Asagi
description:
The heroine of the game Disgaea Wars (Tentative),
a a determined girl who has dedicated to
defeating the Overlord and freeing the world from his clutches.

name: Gordon
description: The 37th Defender of Earth. Defeated by Laharl and made his vassal.

name: Jennifer
description: A genius who earned her doctorate at the age of 10. She made Thursday the robot at the age of 5.

name: Mr. Champloo
description:
An esteemed delinquent teacher
who has dedicated his ardor to cooking.
He is a master of the Grand Fire Chaos Punch.

name: Yukimaru
description: Kunoichi of Snow Melody Village who's known  for adding "Zam" at the end of every sentence. The only flaw in her character is that  she feels responsible for every incident and is always trying to commit suicide.

name: Fubuki
description: Yukimaru's big brother. Devoted to the reconstruction  of Snow Melody Village. He's got a nice voice.

name: Awakened Rozalin
class_name_2: A Past That Must Be Forgotten
description: Rozalin, with the God of All Overlords' power awakened within her. She's surrounded by an ominous aura  that overwhelms her enemies.

name: Justice Flonne
description: Flonne with her Justice Power awakened. The Hammer of Justice takes aim at the wicked Netherworld!

name: Pleinair
description: The mascot of Haradaya, the official website of Harada the character designer. Been working as the receptionist of the Dark Assembly for years.

name: Dark Santa Laharl
description: Changing into a Christmas costume  does not change Laharl's personality. Presents are not to be given away, they are to be taken away!

name: Noel
description: She is a Mage girl who longs to be Santa Claus. She's all dressed up and ready to go. Let's go distribute presents!

name: Attired Rozalin
class_name_5: Sinful Rose of the New Year
description: Rozalin, dressed in the traditional attire  of Snow Melody Village. She's very excited about having a Hatsumoude date  with Adell.

name: Pure Sicily
description: Sicily as the Magic Cutie of Love and Justice. She claims to feel embarrassed, but gets used to  the fluttery and frilly costume really fast.

name: Dark Artina
description: Artina as a Magic Cutie. Mysterious yet sexy, not bad at all.

name: Love Oracle
description: A Magic Cutie who claims to have been born in a dandelion. Boy, girl, who really cares?  What matters is we all love Magic Cuties!

name: Bunny Seraphina
description: Seraphina, the Gorgeous Overlord, has come for Easter in a bunny suit. It looks like she's looking for a capable servant!

name: Easter Mao
description: Mao in his Easter costume. The Easter Eggs he made with his 1.8 Million Evil Quotient... What is he going to do with them?

name: Gym Shorts Fuka
description: Fuka in short shorts is going to take part in the Fest-evil of Sport. She has no doubt she'll win because it's "in her dream". Nevertheless, she's still gonna put in the effort.

name: Ayame
description: The knight of steel who's been appointed the cheerleader of the Fest-evil of Sport. She likes to wear boys' uniform, and can't even sleep without it on.

name: Virunga
description: The Archangel who protects the order of Celestia  with her own justice. Capable as she is, her values are a bit biased.

name: Torachiyo
description:
A battle-hardened adventurer
who has dedicated her entire life to rice balls.
She literally cares about nothing but rice balls. Someone calling out for the King of Rice Balls?!

name: Dias
description:
A self-proclaimed fallen angel hunter who is terrible at acting.
A top-notch gunslinger,
he will finish off his prey before they can even react.

name: Lucy
description:
A fallen angel who claims to be the best undercover investigator.
Although she knows what it takes to be an undercover agent,
she always thinks of just wiping out her enemies when her cover is blown.

name: Swimsuit Girl Laharl
description:
The same tragedy happened again? This time, even Girl Laharl was
forced to wear a swimsuit. She's taking out all her anger for
being converted into a busty hot girl!

name: Swimsuit Etna
description:
Etna who has put on a swimsuit to enjoy the sea.
Beach volleyball, parasol, and scuba...
Get everything ready before fully enjoying the sea. Come and have some fun!

name: Swimsuit Flonne
description:
Flonne is in her swimsuit, ready for sea-bathing.
It seems she has regained her angel identity...Hmm?
You ask me why? Because that's the power of the swimsuit!!

name: Meaver
description:
A tough hunter who hunts monsters all over the Netherworld.
This time, the target is a monster in the sea.
She has changed to her swimsuit in order to keep her spirits high.

name: Marlene
description:
The owner of the Sea Club. Her Sea Club is always crowded,
though Merlin hasn't realized that many of her customers
only come to her club because of her. She is said to be a miser.

name: Fuka XENO
description:
A mysterious girl who looks like Fuka.
She has cut off her long hair due to some... well, very complicated reason.
But that story will be told another time...

name: Raspberyl XENO
description:
Another Raspberyl from another world.
She likes taking selfies with her "cellphone", an essential item for hotties
and then uploading the photos somewhere.

name: Yukata Valvatorez
description:
Valvatorez in his yukata, maintaining the order of the summer fest.
He really enjoys the Sardine Summer Fest he organizes.
In addition, he's asking everyone to greet each other with "Sardine!!"

name: Yukata Yukimaru
description:
Yukimaru wearing her yukata, looking forward to the summer fest.
Although the summer festival was not what she expected,
it was one of the best memories she had with her friends.

name: Hibana
description:
The ultimate firework engineer who applies Nether Science to her fireworks.
She doesn't care if her yukata gets messy
when she is totally absorbed in her firework research.

name: Meliodas
description:
The Dragon's Sin of Wrath
and captain of the Seven Deadly Sins,
as well as the owner of the renowned tavern Boar Hat.

name: Elizabeth
description:
The third adoptive princess
of the Kingdom of Liones has a caring heart.

name: Ban
description:
The Fox's Sin of Greed of the Seven Deadly Sins,
known for his fox-patterned tattoo
and his immortality.

name: Diane
description:
The Serpent's Sin of Envy of the Seven Deadly Sins,
a member of
the Giant Clan.

name: Gowther
description:
The Goat's Sin of Lust
of the Seven Deadly Sins.

name: Cutie Demon Elizabeth
description:
Elizabeth who is wearing Etna's costume,
ready for a fashion contest in another world.
Her determination is unstoppable!

name: Liones Princess Etna
description:
Etna who is wearing Elizabeth's costume,
ready for a fashion contest in another world.
This actually... looks great!

name: Merlin
description:
The Boar's Sin of Gluttony of the Seven Deadly Sins.
She is regarded as the
greatest sorceress in Britannia.

name: King
description:
The Grizzly's Sin of Sloth of the Seven Deadly Sins,
and the king of fairies.

name: Cute Flonne
description:
The much-loved leader of the Cutie V!
With a heart of love and justice, Cute Flonne
has been spreading the greatness of love to the entire world.

name: Cute Chacha
description:
A reserve member of the Cutie V
who loves living a carefree life. After hearing that she could enjoy as much catnip
and other snacks as she pleases, she joined the Cutie V.

name: Cute Merlin
description:
A reserve member of the Cutie V,
she will add mustard sauce to whatever she eats. Her love for mustard sauce is so overwhelming
that she has even invented her own spells to protect it.

name: Mao XENO
description:
Another Mao from another world.
He has invented his own evil gymnastics
and will work out whenever he's idle. By the way, he's nicknamed "Mao Mao".

name: Halloween Majorita
description:
Majorita in disguise as a witch.
She wants to fully enjoy herself
with her most creative Halloween pranks.

name: Halloween Artina
description:
A blood-stained angel descends on Halloween night.
The costume and all accessories are made by Artina herself.
And of course, the blood is fake, too.

name: Halloween Laharl
description:
Laharl who has been turnedinto a Frankenstein by Jennifer.
He buzzes like the real Frankenstein!

name: Zed
description:
A zombie boy who uses a teleportation spell called "Super Reincarnation"
to travel across Netherworlds on his quest to defeat the God of Destruction.
He will never give up even if he dies thousands of times.

name: Majolene
description:
A great witch, as well as the principal of the Magimage School of Magic.
She uses the legendary Magical Wand of Transformation
to become Magic Cutie  Majolene and kick butt!!

name: Attired Killia
description:
To commemorate the first anniversary of Disgaea RPG,
Killia has put on the attire Seraphina ordered for him.
This outfit is actually perfect for strenuous exercise.

name: Attired Seraphina
description:
Seraphina wearing her attire to commemorate
the first anniversary of Disgaea RPG.
Her gown is expensive enough to buy a dozen Netherworlds.

name: Thunderlord Laharl
description:
Another Laharl who wields the power of lightning, known as "Thunderlord".
His serious disposition makes him not really look like a demon.
It seems he comes to this Netherworld for his beloved sister Sicily.

name: Sicily XENO
description:
Another Sicily from another world,
who has dressed as an Overlord. She doesn't appear to be
fond of her meddlesome brother Laharl, but in fact...

name: Xmas Adell
description:
Adell has become stronger thanks to
the Christmas Power granted by Noel.
His bag is filled with
gifts for his cherished one.

name: Xmas Rozalin
description:
Encouraged by her childhood friend Tinker,
Rozalin puts on her Christmas costume and attends a Christmas party.
Although shes a bit embarrassed,
she is looking forward to Adell's reaction.

name: Attired Girl Laharl
description:
For Laharl, this is the ultimate disaster! Once again, he
has been turned into a girl. As an Overlord, she intentionally messed up
her attire as her form of protest.

name: Maiden Sicily
description:
Sicily who has accepted Prinny God's divine power and awakened.
Her new power allows her to skillfully control her shikigami,
helping her brother who is in distress.

name: Tyrant Overlord Laharl
description:
Laharl unleashes his full potential and becomes the Tyrant Overlord.
With his unbridled power, ambition and wildness, he is more than competent as the ruler of the Netherworld.

name: Melodia
description:
A princess from the musical world
who has been waiting for her Prince Charming
and longing for her happy ending.

name: Ivar
description:
The self-proclaimed greatest Overlord in the entire universe.
Despite his stupidity that denies him any respect, he does possess amazing power.
By the way, he likes Bieko the most.

name: Prism Red
description: Prism Red of the Prism Rangers. The hot-blooded one with a strong sense of justice.

name: Prism Blue
description: Prism Blue of the Prism Rangers. He's the cool one and was once Red's Rival.

name: Prism Yellow
description: Prism Yellow of the Prism Rangers. A foodie who loves curry.

name: Prism Green
description: Prism Green of the Prism Rangers. A timid nerd who loves science.

name: Prism Purple
description: Prism Purple of the Prism Rangers. A man with a girl's heart. Actually he's the oldest one among the rangers.

name: Prism Orange
description: Prism Orange of the Prism Rangers. An exotic traveler. He loves fun stuff.

name: Prism Indigo
description: Prism Indigo of the Prism Rangers. Just a commoner. He is bothered by his very existence.

name: Prism Pink
description: Prism Pink of the Prism Rangers. Just a commoner. He is bothered by his very existence.

name: Prism White
description: Prism White of the Prism Rangers. Just a commoner. He is bothered by his very existence.

name: Prism Black
description: Prism Black of the Prism Rangers. Just a commoner. He is bothered by his very existence.

name: Kyoko Needleworker
description: An earnest ninja girl who attends Evil Academy. She's strong-minded and loves knitting.

name: Asuka Cranekick
description: A polite samurai girl who attends Evil Academy. She's quiet and enjoys folding paper cranes.

name: Lanzarote
description: A popular Netherworld idol who sings and dances. She aims for the throne of the Overlord in secret. Stars fly about when she speaks.

name: Alfonzo
description: null_s

name: Beheritas
description: One of the Ten Asura Kings of a the powerful Roaring Rampant Netherworld. Survived a brutal battle royale with his brothers to become a Demon General. Now acts as a loyal servant to Void Dark.

name: Panchos
description: Former underlings of Red Magnus, Overlord of Scorching Flame. He joined the Lost as he had had enough of the Overlord's selfishness. He holds a grudge for being bossed around and treated like a slave.

name: Logan
description: The Blood Parch Overlord, who's feared as the "Throwing Devil Overlord". He is now too old to keep up his strength. He hates the Lost for taking everything from him.

name: Warrior
description: A warrior with a strong body and an indomitable spirit. A professional at close quarters combat.

name: Lady Fighter
description: A female warrior with both flexibility and strength. Excels at one-point blitzkrieg combat.

name: Martial Artist
description: A martial artist who has mastered the physical arts. His unique attire is a traditional costume that  is testament to the legacy of his ancestors.

name: Fight Mistress
description: A female martial artist with fancy skills. She hails from the small frontier world, the "Village of Beasts".

name: Red Skull
description: An earnest magician boy. Highly intelligent despite his physical weakness.

name: Blue Skull
description: An earnest magician boy. Highly intelligent despite his physical weakness.

name: Green Skull
description: An earnest magician boy. Highly intelligent despite his physical weakness.

name: Star Skull
description: An earnest magician boy. Highly intelligent despite his physical weakness.

name: Red Mage
description: An innocent magician girl. As a female demon, she was born with  a natural talent for magic.

name: Blue Mage
description: An innocent magician girl. As a female demon, she was born with  a natural talent for magic.

name: Green Mage
description: An innocent magician girl. As a female demon, she was born with  a natural talent for magic.

name: Star Mage
description: An innocent magician girl. As a female demon, she was born with  a natural talent for magic.

name: Clergy
description: A priest that punishes himself while healing others. He is a sensible person  who has no prejudice against humans or angels.

name: Cleric
description: A priestess who heals her wounded companions. She follows the scriptures of Vinaya  and is always meditating.

name: Archeress
description: A kind-hearted hunter of the Netherworld. She has a kind of precognition to accurately  predict the wind speed and direction.

name: Thief
description: A thief who risks her life to collect treasures. Second to none when it comes to stealing.

name: Maid
description: A faithful maid to her master. The accuracy of her work is not good enough, but she looks cute when she is focused on her work.

name: Gunner
description: A gunman who dispatches his enemies with quick movement. He has the trust of his friends, but he does  not talk much and prefers to be alone.

name: Ninja
description: A cold-hearted assassin who lives in the shadows. He specializes in his unique fighting technique, "Ninja Art".

name: Lady Samurai
description: A sword maiden who exorcises demons. Her clan guards the sanctuary around the Gate of Celestia, the door that connects the Netherworld and Celestia.

name: Armor Knight
description: A knight of steel who boasts an ironclad defense. Admired by children for wielding his sword  and protecting his master.

name: Magic Knight
description: Skilled in both sword and magic, such talent  is rare even among demons.

name: Professor
description: A researcher of magic science. It's said that great cares are taken on experiment subjects.

name: Sage
description: A child of wisdom raised by a Nether Tree who's lived for 100 million years. She can hear the voice of plants and trees and has a close relationship with fairies.

name: Wrestler
description: A warrior who spends his days fighting the strong. He excels at fighting in pairs.

name: Pirate
description: A pirate who runs through the vast universe. He excels at long-range sniping.

name: Dark Knight
description: A knight in black who controls the darkness. The jet-black flames flickering in the depths of his eyes  would bring the fear of death to anyone who sees the flames.

name: Kunoichi
description: The beautiful Kunoichi dances in the darkness. She plays the enemy with her phantom-like movements.

name: Sorcerer
description: A spell caster who spreads misery around. She has her own definition of good and evil and believes that  her mission is to control the misery of others.

name: Onmyo Monk
description: A spell caster who controls the fields with his unique ability. His power is deemed moderate, but many appreciate the potential that his abilities hold.

name: Beastmaster
description: A wild warrior who lives with Monsters. She is passionate about breeding the best Monsters, and no one outperforms her in terms of  knowledge and skills.

name: Masked Hero
description: An unidentified wannabe hero. His ability to escape is unrivalled.

name: Android
description: Weaponry designed in a female form. The armor is made of a special metal, making it highly durable and flexible.

name: Bouncer
description: A guardian dressed in a black suit. He has a strong spirit and will use his own body  to shield his master.

name: Battle Suit
description: A powerful battle suit made by humans. It increases the stats of its user a lot.

name: Gustak Soldier
description: Soldiers who come from an empire in the cold regions of the Human World. He can't put on his armor by himself.

name: Lekidona Soldier
description: Soldier who comes from an empire in the desert regions of the Human World. He has strong legs and feet thanks to his training in the sand.

name: Celestial Host
description: Heavenly soldier specializing in battle. He upholds the heavenly law and  ruthlessly eliminates those who oppose it.

name: Celestial Hostess
description: A female soldier who protects the celestial peace. Because of her firm beliefs, she is a bit stubborn in certain ways.

name: Dead Pirate
description: This dead demon is controlled by others. It has no thoughts and just fights as commanded.

name: Dead Knight
description: This dead demon is controlled by others. It has no thoughts and just fights as commanded.

name: Dead Sage
description: This dead demon is controlled by others. It has no thoughts and just fights as commanded.

name: EDF Soldier
description: It is the second most coveted occupation for boys, after the Defender of Earth. Not only is he skilled with axes and guns, he is also an excellent fighter with fists.

name: EDF Soldier
description: It is the second most coveted occupation for boys, after the Defender of Earth. Not only is he skilled with axes and guns, he is also an excellent fighter with fists.

name: EDF Soldier
description: It is the second most coveted occupation for boys, after the Defender of Earth. Not only is he skilled with axes and guns, he is also an excellent fighter with fists.

name: EDF Soldier
description: It is the second most coveted occupation for boys, after the Defender of Earth. Not only is he skilled with axes and guns, he is also an excellent fighter with fists.

name: Usalia
description: Toto Bunny Overlord, affected by the curse of berserk. She suppresses the curse by eating curry. She's a well-behaved girl with a strong will.

name: Raspberyl
description: She's a graduate of Evil Academy and now a Delinquent Teacher. She's a super Delinquent who works every day raising money, donating blood, and engaging in volunteer work. A life rebelling against demon conventions sure looks cool.

name: Desco
description: A girl created to destroy the world. Her dream is to become the strongest Final Boss in the world. She admires Fuka as her Big Sis.

name: Des X
description: The Final Boss and the ultimate weapon created by Genjuro Kazamatsuri, DESCO, Perfect Version. The true culprit who hated and killed Fuka.

name: Prinny Kurtis
description: This green Prinny is working as a Defender of Earth. He tries hard to add "dood" to the end of every sentence.

name: Pringer V3
description: The deadliest robot ever found in the Prinny world. Only disciplined Prinnies can become robots.... It looks just like a Prinny, but it doesn't explode when thrown.

name: Hugo
description: The Netherworld President, who reigns over all demons. He's Emizel's Father. Is he the cause of all this corruption...?

name: Thursday
description: An all-purpose robot made by Jennifer. It is equipped with a computerized voice and a self-destruct mechanism.

name: Taro
description: A timid and cynical person, Adell's younger brother. He has horns on his head due to the curse of Overlord Zenon. He admires and respects Rozalin.

name: Hanako
description: The younger sister of Adell and Taro, who's shy but energetic. She has wings on her back due to the curse of Overlord Zenon. Despite her young age, her cooking skills are on par with the professionals.

name: Tink
description: Rozalin's childhood friend and subordinate of Overlord Zenon. He used to be a handsome boy, but somehow was turned into a frog.

name: Red Tink
description: Rozalin's childhood friend and subordinate of Overlord Zenon. Normally a gentle demon, but when enraged, he becomes violent and dangerous.

name: Vulcanus
description: This archangel is jealous of Flonne, who's favored by the Seraph. He lost himself in ambition and anger and has gone haywire.

name: Kurtis
description: He was caught up in an incident and lost 70% of his body. He's a cyborg who calls himself the Defender of Earth.

name: Lamington
description: Lamington is the High Seraph of Celestia. He sent Flonne to the Netherworld to carry out a secret plan.

name: Don Joaquin
class_name_5: The Glorious First Defender of Earth
description: The First Hero of the Netherworld. Unable to fulfill his mission, his regrets have driven his soul to wander the Netherworld.

name: Mid-Boss
description: A mysterious demon who's often called  Mid-Boss by Laharl and his friends. He calls himself Vyers the Dark Adonis, but that name is not generally accepted by others.

name: Ms. Raspberyl
description: She's a graduate of Evil Academy and now a Delinquent Teacher. She's a super Delinquent who works every day raising money, donating blood, and engaging in volunteer work. A life rebelling against demon conventions sure looks cool.

name: Santa Usalia
class_name_1: Rabbit Overlord of the Holy Night
class_name_2: Rabbit Overlord of the Holy Night
description: It's nice to get dressed, but Usalia  doesn't know what Christmas is all about. So she decides to go distribute curry.

name: Mirror Cake Prinny
description: Prinnies that look happy. But their actual condition  is too dark to divulge...

name: Gym Shorts Raspberyl

name: Overlord Asagi
description:
The evil Overlord that rules the world of "Disgaea Wars (Tentative)".
With her absolute power,
she dominates the world, threatening all its denizens.

name: Game Developer Asagi
description:
The genius girl who developed the game Disgaea Wars (Tentative).
In order to develop interesting games,
her brain is always running at full capacity. For her, a continuous intake of sugar is a must!

name: Swimsuit Desco
description:
Desco, who is in her special swimsuit and can dive for an extremely long time.
She loves to leave only her fin above the surface of the water,
pretending to be a shark.

name: Desco XENO
description:
Another Desco from another world.
She's been working hard to help Fuka XENO.
Rumor has it that she has already become the final boss in her world?

name: Swimsuit Prinny
description:
A Prinny who is determined to enjoy his summer vacation,
but his summer vacation
is doomed to be torture...

name: Attired Prinny
description:
A prinny wearing his attire to commemorate the first anniversary
of Disgaea RPG. This Prinny's back looks slightly straighter than usual,
perhaps because of this splendid attire.

name: Dark Santa Usalia
description:
Usalia inherits
Laharl's Dark Santa suit and becomes ruthless.
No longer confined by her amiable disposition,
she is incredibly powerful.

name: Liezerota
description:
A very gentle-looking woman.
She is the daughter of Goldion the Great Demon Fist, and the elder sister of Void.
She treats Killia like family.

name: Saint Etna
description:
Another Etna from another world.
Despite being a demon,
she has a gentle disposition and a heart of gold.
Her saintly voice has surprised even Prinnies.

name: Sakuya
description:
A battle-hardened nine-tailed fox who has made divination her life's work.
She is a troublemaker, as she will curse those who get terrible divination results,
and grant her favor to those who get ideal results.

name: Pringer X
description:
The pinnacle of ancient civilizations.
This legendary Prinny-shaped robot is a killing machine
as it has shed blood in countless battles.

name: Grosso
description: A demon who was a vassal of the late King Krichevskoy. He was known as a chief strategist and commanded battles. ... or so it's said. Now no one remembers the details.

description: A demon who was a vassal of the late King Krichevskoy. She was favored for her ability as a treasure hunter. It's said that she took good care of Laharl.

name: Hoggmeiser
description: A rich demon who loves money and his son. He produces idols and makes a killing. Put "$" at the end of every sentence and you can imitate him!
